800
00:53:09,180 --> 00:53:11,440
Ce bâtard n'aura pas d'argent.

801
00:53:13,900 --> 00:53:14,860
Do San.

802
00:53:16,570 --> 00:53:20,070
Merci. Merci infiniment, Do San.

803
00:53:20,150 --> 00:53:21,780
Merci

